0.3.0       Thu Jul  6 09:18:03 CDT 2023
========================================
[ENHANCEMENTS]
The new $HTML::Scrape::WARNINGS variable lets you suppress warnings in
the scraper.

[FIXES]
Aad spaces to text scraping that includes <br> or <hr>.

Handle empty tags with IDs.


